{"tid":2445564,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"關於業報法則的推論","createTime":"2021-03-13T17:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T13:08:48.000Z","uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9249aec7352cc76dc92eacb49b66ef436a191f0b","tid":2445564,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:00:42.000Z","msg":"基於回力鏢打出一個，就食返一個的基本債銷循環<br />\n<br />\n以下是電影有一些橋段的概念有點不合理的：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YcaTovccBOI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYcaTovccBOI&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=12c30287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YcaTovccBOI</a><br />\n<br />\n例如有人極為懶惰，他就會受懶惰報，即是會出現被懶惰人拖累的情況，即是不能成功奴役他人，而不是被人成功壓迫奴役<br />\n<br />\n其他一切亦如是"},{"pid":"73735c7e7db72a986db1b577df0decab4e68aa5a","tid":2445564,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1_GbsxxBD0Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1_GbsxxBD0Q&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=4048943a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1_GbsxxBD0Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S_V3B-mgJgU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS_V3B-mgJgU&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=c4e4dd7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S_V3B-mgJgU</a><br />\n<br />\n這似乎也是不合理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於佛法義理，佛陀聖律：<br />\n<br />\n拔舌地獄當由真的把人的舌頭血腥拔出的惡人所受<br />\n<br />\n而惡口妄語人應當進入惡口妄語地獄"},{"pid":"1e587318d295cc7ecf82f3502f7b283452571a56","tid":2445564,"uid":161398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"就咁睇 好多人落硬地獄咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2b9e84d3f02cd3fd5fcf84e026288b7e3b2df0","tid":2445564,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:31:17.000Z","msg":"貪錢貪女色的連登仔一定很快有業報"},{"pid":"53b9565993549988e58ef89a977b6b58a9d20a44","tid":2445564,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e587318d295cc7ecf82f3502f7b283452571a56","tid":2445564,"uid":161398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"就咁睇 好多人落硬地獄咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:31:24.000Z","msg":"傳播佛法的最大障礙之一，就是太多電影或youtube片或小說，散播嚴重違返佛陀聖訓義理的思想"},{"pid":"f18fff45880d3f9428a8b809d850074e940ece3a","tid":2445564,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53b9565993549988e58ef89a977b6b58a9d20a44","tid":2445564,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e587318d295cc7ecf82f3502f7b283452571a56","tid":2445564,"uid":161398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"就咁睇 好多人落硬地獄咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:31:24.000Z","msg":"傳播佛法的最大障礙之一，就是太多電影或youtube片或小說，散播嚴重違返佛陀聖訓義理的思想"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:38:30.000Z","msg":"例如呢"},{"pid":"119527a045dee2c2c8522b46cc1940d4d4e3d0c7","tid":2445564,"uid":47901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f18fff45880d3f9428a8b809d850074e940ece3a","tid":2445564,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53b9565993549988e58ef89a977b6b58a9d20a44","tid":2445564,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e587318d295cc7ecf82f3502f7b283452571a56","tid":2445564,"uid":161398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"就咁睇 好多人落硬地獄咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:31:24.000Z","msg":"傳播佛法的最大障礙之一，就是太多電影或youtube片或小說，散播嚴重違返佛陀聖訓義理的思想"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:38:30.000Z","msg":"例如呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:10:57.000Z","msg":"例如這一個，<br />\n<a href=\"https://y