樣，充滿盼望，幻想，開心到唔願訓覺，或像毒男就黎見女神一樣<br />\n<br />\n死亡的問題不就解決了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n在神 的設局，有一種現象，我稱之為&ldquo;囚徒逆轉&rdquo;，是設置在人的心理規則中，&ldquo;囚徒逆轉&rdquo;現象的表現形式，在於人雖戰勝了一切，似是勝過所有敵人，勝過天地，勝過物質資源的貧乏，但卻被自己的心靈鎖死，而這個鎖比所有高設防的監牢還要堅固好多好多倍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c4Qap03dvMo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc4Qap03dvMo&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=b97ffb4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c4Qap03dvMo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8YZm9F50Jm0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8YZm9F50Jm0&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=198da27c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8YZm9F50Jm0</a>"},{"pid":"e86b8c7a43656a1f2ea42450556dc9055e32d634","tid":2445564,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f1ff943a2a0adb83fd0c7ade73b434d52a938008","tid":2445564,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"70b898a1cea7a8e7e698b62446ea90f61140ef0a","tid":2445564,"uid":161398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c512c548e478596e16e88791f344d8a958d69674","tid":2445564,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6CnQDDT2ryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6CnQDDT2ryc&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=889b381e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6CnQDDT2ryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cE4gLA6WPRM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcE4gLA6WPRM&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=06c1cba6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cE4gLA6WPRM</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:31:05.000Z","msg":"做梗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:43:10.000Z","msg":"誇張的假設（如有雷同實屬巧合）<br />\n<br />\n對於美國有錢佬對死